description:
go.codereview: trivial change to unblock dashboard

The dashboard has stopped accepting results for this subrepo. To avoid taking more drastic steps, CL 6858094, I'd like to make a small commit to see if it gets it going again.

messages.text:
LGTM

sure, okay. But fixing the dashboard to not store over a MB of
redundant data is the right solution.

Yes, see the CL linked. The weird thing is, best I can tell, the data
stored on that result key is ~800kb.
